  "key_insight": "Median outcome is Jul 31, 2026. 95% confidence is Sep 24, 2026. The gap between 50% and 85% is the wait-cost of being predictable \u2014 wider gap = more daily-throughput variance.",
  "next_actions": [
    "Commit externally on the 85% date (Sep 2, 2026), not the 50% date (Jul 31, 2026).",
